How do I design with minimal content?

Designing was troublesome with no current photographs, so I opt to using content posted on their Facebook.

Since they had a professional video, I used that as a focal point for users to seek the business.

The rest of the website was designed based on more of a “classy” look and feel.

How should I implement the application forms?

Formacade helps the recruitment forms accessible to other employees. With having the online form connect with a Google Form, it can be shared and edited with ease. Implementing Formacade was optimal because it did not push back the duration of development.

Conclusion

Even with minimal content, I was able to design and execute a product that provided great value. Within the first week there were over seven work applications, providing more work diversity.
